challenges.mission_1_november:
Find any 10 different trees or shrubs from the following types:

-Pines, conifers, yews, and podocarps;
-Palms;
-Beeches, walnuts, and oaks;
-Maples, buckeyes, mangos, mahoganies, and citrus;
-Hollies;
-Rowans, Whitebeams;
-Cherries, apples, and pears;
-Hackberries, aspens, poplars, and willows;
-Laurels, avocado, spicebush, and sassafrass;
-Elms;
-Buckthorns and Ceanothus;
-Figs and mulberries;
-Mangroves;
-Bushwillows;
-Dogwoods, hydrangeas, and tupelos

